reviewText:
Dont buy this online. Just go to Wal-mart and go to the $1 dvd section new the registers and they have all 3 dvds for $1. People are tring to sell them for like $25 rip off!

Don't believe me go look thats where i got mine WAL-MART!
Each DVD only has a few minutes of Lamb Chop, Hush Puppy or Charlie Horse.  This is from Shari's show in the 60s, NOT the 90s.
